caption.text:
✨️🇳‌🇪‌🇼‌ 🇨‌🇭‌🇦‌🇱‌🇱‌🇪‌🇳‌🇬‌🇪‌✨️

#AloGlowUp
17-24 September 

Each day we explore a duality: strength and softness, grounding and expansion, focus and flow…
The practice is about finding the balance point between seemingly opposite energies. We'll move with intention, styled in Alo, aligning breath, movement, and meaning.

✨️ ᒪIᑎᗴ ᑌᑭ ✨️

• Day 1 – Root & Rise: Root into presence and rise into possibility.
Pose: Grounded pose

• Day 2 – Strength & Suppleness: Be strong and soft. Let both coexist.
Pose: Arm balance 

• Day 3 – Focus & Flow: Move with direction and stay steady within motion.
Pose: Hip opener 

• Day 4 – Courage & Surrender: Open your heart—it’s the strongest thing you can do.
Pose: Heart opener 

• Day 5 – Lightness & Stability: Trust your foundation, then take flight.
Pose: Standing balance

• Day 6 – Silence & Expression: Listen first. Feel deeply. Speak from truth.
Pose: Creative variation pose.

• Day 7 – Light & Shadow: Honor every side of yourself. Both are sacred.
Pose: Twist pose 

• Day 8 – Inner Equilibrium: Come home to yourself—balance lives within.
Pose: Inverted balance.

 𝕊ℙ𝕆ℕ𝕊𝕆ℝ𝔼𝔻 𝔹𝕐 @aloyoga & @alomoves 🛍

🧘🏻‍♀️ ℍ𝕆𝕊𝕋𝕊 🧘🏻‍♀️

@rhythm_of_yoga 
@yooga_land 
@yoga.nerea 
@movewithimma 
@deehollidayyoga 

📜 FOLLOW all rules, and ALL in this post:
1) Tag the team and sponsor in all posts for each day. You must follow hosts and sponsor.
2) REPOST the flyer to your main page (not story and not carousel)
3) Engage with others by encouraging them each day of this challenge (without this, you may not be considered to win)
4.) Post each day using ONLY this challenge #AloGlowUp .
Posts with multiple challenge # hastags will not be considered for winning.
